{"whisper":["H829Kq6g80UJ9CuX"],"content":"<div class=\"main-ca\">\n  <p><b>Welcome to Cthulhu Architect's</b></p>\n  <p><b>Free Modern Maps</b></p>\n  <hr />\n  <p>Included you will find 16 free unique locations (20 total maps) to use in your modern game!</p>\n  <p>If you are using 'Multilevel Tokens' foundry module then your players can move freely in other floors.</p>\n  <p>On my Patreon page you can find many more maps which include many variations and in many cases even floor plans. You will also find many tokens/tiles in the paddings of my maps so you can style them according to your needs.</p>\n  <p>If you want to get my full collection of 100+ unique locations, you can <br /><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cthulhu_architect\">subscribe on my patreon page</a></p>\n  <p>You can view a gallery of all my maps on my <a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/cthulhu_architect/cthulhu-architect-modern-maps/\">Pinterest</a></p>\n  <p>Check out my <a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/packages/cthulhu-architect-handout-generator-lite\">\"Handout Generator\" foundry module</a> and create fast &amp; easily handouts for your game</p>\n  <p>Find out more about my work on <a href=\"https://cthulhuarchitect.com\">my website</a></p>\n  <p>Did you find a bug? You can find me on <a href=\"https://discord.gg/2tgye4fWpZ\">my Discord server</a>.</p>\n</div>","type":0,"user":"H829Kq6g80UJ9CuX","timestamp":1678291272264,"flavor":"","speaker":{"scene":null,"actor":null,"token":null,"alias":""},"blind":false,"rolls":[],"sound":null,"emote":false,"flags":{},"_id":"HeTOCWLINcgJXIxb"}
